{"tid":1907900,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「僅北海道認事態嚴重！」觀察家：日本政府低估感染數，2周後疫情恐大爆發","createTime":"2020-03-03T02:09:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-03T11:17:32.000Z","uid":184679,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b4dbfc84279c023fcbd940227ab97125ddc96fb1","tid":1907900,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T02:09:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://image.cache.storm.mg/styles/smg-800x533-fp/s3/media/image/2020/03/02/20200302-063329_U1085_M595489_fbc3.jpg?itok=rlYirJ7G\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.cache.storm.mg%2Fstyles%2Fsmg-800x533-fp%2Fs3%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2020%2F03%2F02%2F20200302-063329_U1085_M595489_fbc3.jpg%3Fitok%3DrlYirJ7G&h=f37f1803&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖為北海道知事鈴木直道。（資料照，美聯社）<br />\n<br />\n日本政經觀察家福澤喬2日於《POP搶先爆》接受主持人朱學恒專訪時表示，日本官方確診人數不可全信，這2周將是日本武漢肺炎（新冠肺炎）疫情關鍵時刻，若是情況不樂觀，恐將迅速爆發。<br />\n<br />\n許多網友提問，究竟日韓哪國較為嚴重？福澤喬表示，南韓目前全面擴大檢驗，開放多個檢測中心，每日可檢驗7萬個疑似病例，速度相當快，但可能出現誤診情形，預計將高估確診人數；另一方面，日本檢測中心少，檢測門檻高（需有明確旅遊史與接觸史），容易低估感染人數，若是情況嚴重，未來將一次性大爆發。<br />\n<br />\n日本中央與地方政策不同調<br />\n<br />\n除了檢測效率低落，日本近日亦出現中央與地方政策不同步的問題，先前中央政府指示，必須停課到3月下旬，北陸石川縣金澤市卻決定照常上課。1月28日內閣通過法案，將武漢肺炎列為強制管理傳染病，該法案卻要1周後才能施行，缺乏彈性，唯有北海道承認事態嚴重，獨自進入緊急狀態。<br />\n<br />\n福澤喬表示，200萬人參加的札幌雪祭為北海道拉起警報的原因，北海道許多感染者皆參加過該祭典，從工作人員到小吃攤，皆有感染風險。北海道知事鈴木直道因為年輕，未受日本官僚系統影響，反而真正掌握了所有狀況，提前囤積口罩並要求居民盡量減少出門。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.storm.mg/article/2353998\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.storm.mg%2Farticle%2F2353998&d=FoM%2FNT%2BxDvRLDdkWKwCN%2BL32HZRMtn4xjJY4gFhUisg%3D&h=fc97ac1e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.storm.mg/article/2353998</a>"},{"pid":"62571b57452cee23be57a887493ef8251fc93857","tid":1907900,"uid":72009,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T02:15:53.000Z","msg":"估計拍群交AV遲早出事，1人感染幾十人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6ff7c37d0b7bf7080c00abef061f26d733ed5fc","tid":1907900,"uid":21545,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T02:22:29.000Z","msg":"全日本得一個人面對現實<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f43c3363bc1f60496e40b5d01a51bfe6d5c9146","tid":1907900,"uid":64191,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T02:30:51.000Z","msg":"550年前： 應仁文明之亂、明應政變引發戰國時代<br />\n今日：武漢肺炎引發地方割據<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"450d19977719ce5e9a8229cb2b1ec79012502ab5","tid":1907900,"uid":284652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T02:36:32.000Z","msg":"知事靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14d28f85c5e47888b2831878d1b997b72198d82c","tid":1907900,"uid":62721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T02:42:23.000Z","msg":"搵返D專家處理啦，仲玩官僚就日本沉沒啦日本仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13d4732cf0745d420d3170a827a57c0ed8b788a4","tid":1907900,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T02:54:20.000Z","msg":"老人家死撚晒等後生d上場"},{"pid":"1fa8af93f666934480357cf9ac7c594d42dc54c5","tid":1907900,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T04:53:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"442284f0865ebd444971269dd96ec27b1a2938b5","tid":1907900,"uid":22869,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T06:15:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"033988c624df6ba8975c0915147737f89889542f","tid":1907900,"uid":41818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T06:24:01.000Z","msg":"呢個好似係日本最後生知事"},{"pid":"2b06a6e26ab2c2c8d8787d0948900612d8d3756f","tid":1907900,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"033988c624df6ba8975c0915147737f89889542f","tid":1907900,"uid":41818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T06:24:01.000Z","msg":"呢個好似係日本最後生知事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T06:26:41.000Z","msg":"做官都係衛生局出身"},{"pid":"652f069569e68504196e552d17f417e49d78b816","tid":1907900,"uid":392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T06:29:22.000Z","msg":"北海道知事鈴木直道因為年輕，未受日本官僚系統影響，反而真正掌握了所有狀況，提前囤積口罩並要求居民盡量減少出門。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c11b9ae71541cac011803be1627b5d37eaeaede1","tid":1907900,"uid":41818,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"2b06a6e26ab2c2c8d8787d0948900612d8d3756f","tid":1907900,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"033988c624df6ba8975c0915147737f89889542f","tid":1907900,"uid":41818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T06:24:01.000Z","msg":"呢個好似係日本最後生知事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T06:26:41.000Z","msg":"做官都係衛生局出身"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T06:32:17.000Z","msg":"衛生醫療背景出身<br />\n<br />\n在日本疫情不斷持續的情況下，北海道確診人數長期在日本各地「名列前茅」。許多人都質疑日本中央政府是為了避免檢測出更多確診人數，導致影響夏季東奧的舉辦。此舉引發日本國民不滿，指責政府應對疫情不力。<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n相較之下，北海道確診人數多，被國內認為是因為檢測積極而有的成果，反而讓人放心。<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n38歲的鈴木直道出身於東京附近，曾長期在東京的地方衛生部門任職。到了2008年，鈴木直道被派往北海道交流任職，幫助重建當時瀕臨破產的夕張市經濟，從此與北海道結緣。<br />\n<br />\n交流任職結束後，鈴木直道辭去已獲晉升的東京都公職，前往夕張市競選市長並一舉成功，成為當時日本最年輕的市長。2019年，鈴木直道又成功競選北海道知事。<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n上任初期的鈴木直道工作重心仍然以振興地方經濟為主，還主動為自己降薪以顯示削減政府開支的誠意。<br />\n<br />\n重點應該係比較有魄力做實事"},{"pid":"6d2e6d33fce4f264347d206938ea765422a3cf65","tid":1907900,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T07:16:43.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"065321c25c71f0c6a5577374d704155b15c17a98","tid":1907900,"uid":301915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T07:17:55.000Z","msg":"唔仆街唔知死，留名等睇第二次大東亞共榮圈"},{"pid":"1da9aaa00d4db31cd73b0e5502ceff48a8777efe","tid":1907900,"uid":80724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T07:29:13.000Z","msg":"睇嚟日本真係要靠支那武漢肺炎洗走一啲廢佬官員，比啲後生嘅上場"},{"pid":"759ad219c9420e3b376e17271b0350eec8d12f8d","tid":1907900,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1da9aaa00d4db31cd73b0e5502ceff48a8777efe","tid":1907900,"uid":80724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T07:29:13.000Z","msg":"睇嚟日本真係要靠支那武漢肺炎洗走一啲廢佬官員，比啲後生嘅上場"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T10:31:14.000Z","msg":"有後生 但估計都係政治世家玩晒多"},{"pid":"339d3e4d712b993ecabce74f89a9b0c62e9a1520","tid":1907900,"uid":25601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"759ad219c9420e3b376e17271b0350eec8d12f8d","tid":1907900,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1da9aaa00d4db31cd73b0e5502ceff48a8777efe","tid":1907900,"uid":80724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T07:29:13.000Z","msg":"睇嚟日本真係要靠支那武漢肺炎洗走一啲廢佬官員，比啲後生嘅上場"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T10:31:14.000Z","msg":"有後生 但估計都係政治世家玩晒多"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T10:33:32.000Z","msg":"好過老人政治"},{"pid":"00776f0495d378becd24c7c90eae99e40fba42cd","tid":1907900,"uid":52056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"339d3e4d712b993ecabce74f89a9b0c62e9a1520","tid":1907900,"uid":25601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"759ad219c9420e3b376e17271b0350eec8d12f8d","tid":1907900,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1da9aaa00d4db31cd73b0e5502ceff48a8777efe","tid":1907900,"uid":80724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T07:29:13.000Z","msg":"睇嚟日本真係要靠支那武漢肺炎洗走一啲廢佬官員，比啲後生嘅上場"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T10:31:14.000Z","msg":"有後生 但估計都係政治世家玩晒多"},"citedBy":1,